# Normalize all text files to LF in the working tree, regardless of host OS
# or the checking-out user's core.autocrlf setting. Without this, a Windows
# host with core.autocrlf=true checks scripts out with CRLF, and since
# .devcontainer/devcontainer.json bind-mounts the live repo straight into
# the Linux container, a CRLF shebang line ("#!/usr/bin/env bash\r") fails
# to run at all.
* text=auto eol=lf

